## Response [/response/]

### Get a Collection of Responses [GET]

+ Parameters
    - limit (integer, optional) - optional used to limit number of returned responses.
    - offset (integer, optional) - used to page and get the next set of responses.
    - tags (string, optional) - Comma demlimted string of tags to filter the responses by.

+ Response 200 (application/json)
{

    "meta": {
        "limit": 2,
        "next": "/api/full/response/?limit=2&offset=17",
